"{\"uid\": \"salon.com-2024-04-22-running-uniform-nike-olympics-controversy\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"\\\"Why is the crotch areaSOsmall?\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 32, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the crotch\", \"from\": 8, \"to\": 18}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My friend and I stood side by side in the track and field office at Columbia University, a cavernous, semi-corporate lair that was part of a network of subterranean passages in the depths of a very old, very grey fitness center.\", \"from\": 34, \"to\": 262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 102, \"end\": 121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.082104852895999e-22, \"text\": \"Columbia University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My friend\", \"from\": 34, \"to\": 43}, {\"ngram\": \"side\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 68}, {\"ngram\": \"the track and field office\", \"from\": 72, \"to\": 98}, {\"ngram\": \"a cavernous, semi-corporate lair\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 155}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 169}, {\"ngram\": \"a network\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 182}, {\"ngram\": \"subterranean passages\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 207}, {\"ngram\": \"the depths\", \"from\": 211, \"to\": 221}, {\"ngram\": \"a very old, very grey fitness center\", \"from\": 225, \"to\": 261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We gazed at the new uniforms New Balance - our team's designated sponsor - had issued.\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 293, \"end\": 304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Balance\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"New Balance\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Balance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Balance\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the new uniforms\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 292}, {\"ngram\": \"our team's designated sponsor\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The singlet was not particularly radical: layered shades of white and Columbia's signature shade, Pantone 292.\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 461, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The singlet\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 362}, {\"ngram\": \": layered shades\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"white and Columbia's signature shade\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"Pantone\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the second portion of our new race gear that had given us pause.\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second portion\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 488}, {\"ngram\": \"our new race gear\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"pause\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As an athlete, you are accustomed to thinking quite a bit about your body.\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"quite a bit\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"your body\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Scattered with imprints of a roaring lion (so faint that they just looked like muted polka-dots), the bottoms had a laughably paltry piece of fabric - something like the width of a large safety pin - to cover our nether regions.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"imprints\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"a roaring lion\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"muted polka-dots\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 707}, {\"ngram\": \"the bottoms\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"a laughably paltry piece\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 750}, {\"ngram\": \"fabric\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"- something\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"the width\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 787}, {\"ngram\": \"a large safety pin\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 809}, {\"ngram\": \"our nether regions\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I recall using the phrase, \\\"reverse thong.\\\"\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the phrase\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"reverse thong\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Buns,\\\" as they are colloquially referred to by runners, are effectively bikini briefs to begin with.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Buns\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"runners\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"bikini briefs\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is not much fabric to play with, let alone shear off.\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1047, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"much fabric\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And yet, Nike somehow managed to whittle down one of those offerings for female track and field athletes competing at the upcoming summer 2024 Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9933015277637895, \"rank\": 0.006743644348500694, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}, {\"begin\": 1209, \"end\": 1214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.73175916546069e-24, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those offerings\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1117}, 