ost\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Men's sports always get more coverage,\\\" another joked wryly.\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Men's sports\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"more coverage\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seattle-based women's running apparel company, Oiselle, jested, \\\"When you run out of fabric after designing the men's kit .\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1901, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Seattle-based women's running apparel company\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"Oiselle\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"fabric\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's kit\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1899}]}, {\"sentence\": \".\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \".\\\"\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A number of professional athletes also spoke out in response to the post to vocalize discontent with the uniform.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 2021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A number\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"professional athletes\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1941}, {\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"the post\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"discontent\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"the uniform\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"U.S. long jumper Tara Davis-Woodhall, who finished sixth at the Tokyo games in 2021, wrote, \\\"Wait my hoo haa is gonna be out.\\\"\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2040, \"end\": 2044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tara_Maclay\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.95723421317376e-12, \"text\": \"Tara\", \"types\": [\"Q950