, \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her comment\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"Citius' post\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2412}, {\"ngram\": \"the upcoming Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Former five-time NCAA champion Lauren Fleshman slammed the leotardon Instagramas \\\"a costume born of patriarchal forces that are no longer welcome or needed to get eyes on women's sports.\\\"\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2510, \"end\": 2523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9394566648603366e-20, \"text\": \"NCAA champion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2524, \"end\": 2539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauren_Fleshman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lauren Fleshman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauren_Fleshman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauren_Fleshman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the leotardon Instagramas\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2573}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"a costume\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2584}, {\"ngram\": \"patriarchal forces\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2611}, {\"ngram\": \"eyes\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2660}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sports\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am sorry, but show me one WNBA or NWSL team who would enthusiastically support this kit,\\\" she wrote.\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2711, \"end\": 2715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.475313253646108e-20, \"text\": \"WNBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2719, \"end\": 2723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6656351218653586e-20, \"text\": \"NWSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this kit\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Women's kits should be in service to performance, mentally and physically.\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2861, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Women's kits\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"service\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2820}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If this outfit was truly beneficial to physical performance, men would wear it.\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this outfit\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"physical performance\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2921}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not an elite athletic kit for track and field.\\\"\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an elite athletic kit\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2975}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 2985}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 2995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fleshman's opinions align with what many others have said since Nike unveiled the uniform.\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3063, \"end\": 3067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9933015277637895, \"rank\": 0.006743644348500694, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fleshman's opinions\", \"from\": 2999, \"to\": 3018}, {\"ngram\": \"many others\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"the uniform\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And for good reason - the norms that govern professional women's sports attire, though graduallyevolving, are still largely dictated by sexist ideals that we have become societally attuned to.\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good reason\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3109}, {\"ngram\": \"the norms\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3121}, {\"ngram\": \"professional women's sports attire\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3168}, {\"ngram\": \"sexist ideals\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the ill-received uniform drop, Nike Chief Innovation Officer John Hoke said in a statement, \\\"Nike designed the Paris 2024 track and field kits to offer athletes a range of silhouettes tailored for various sport disciplines, body types and sizes, prioritizing performance and maximum breathability.\\\"\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3325, \"end\": 3329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9933015277637895, \"rank\": 0.006743644348500694, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}, {\"begin\": 3360, \"end\": 3364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoke_County,_North_Carolina\", \"score\": 0.978058559651503, \"rank\": 0.015444015444015344, \"text\": \"Hoke\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoke_County,_North_Carolina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoke_County,_North_Carolina\"}, {\"begin\": 3387, \"end\": 3391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9933015277637895, \"rank\": 0.006743644348500694, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}, {\"begin\": 3405, \"end\": 3415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.784259895009144e-24, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ill-received uniform drop\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3323}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 3373, \"to\": 3384}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3446, \"to\": 3454}, {\"ngram\": \"a range\", \"from\": 3455, \"to\": 3462}, {\"ngram\": \"silhouettes\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3477}, {\"ngram\": \"various sport disciplines\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3516}, {\"ngram\": \"body types\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3528}, {\"ngram\": \"sizes\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3538}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 3553, \"to\": 3564}, {\"ngram\": \"maximum breathability\", \"from\": 3569, \"to\": 3590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As any runner - professional or not - knows, you run best when you are comfortable and feel empowered.\", \"from\": 3594, \"to\": 3696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's worth noting, then, that many elite women runners are consistently choosing to compete in buns for multiple reasons.\", \"from\": 3697, \"to\": 3818, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many elite women runners\", \"from\": 3727, \"to\": 3751}, {\"ngram\": \"buns\", \"from\": 3792, \"to\": 3796}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple reasons\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 3817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The problem with Nike's leotard selection, insofar as the mannequin shows it, is that it has an unnecessarily soaring cut.\", \"from\": 3819, \"to\": 3941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3836, \"end\": 3840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9933015277637895, \"rank\": 0.006743644348500694, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The problem\", \"from\": 3819, \"to\": 3830}, {\"ngram\": \"the mannequin\", \"from\": 3873, \"to\": 3886}, {\"ngram\": \"an unnecessarily soaring cut\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 3940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the problematic aspect of the Olympic leotard is not merely isolated to sexism.\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 4026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the problematic aspect\", \"from\": 3947, \"to\": 3969}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic leotard\", \"from\": 3973, \"to\": 3992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Revealing and tight uniforms in women's running, comfortable and popular as they may be, can compound body image andeating disorderissues that are already endemic to the sport.\", \"from\": 4027, \"to\": 4203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Revealing and tight uniforms\", \"from\": 4027, \"to\": 4055}, {\"ngram\": \"body image\", \"from\": 4129, \"to\": 4139}, {\"ngram\": \"disorderissues\", \"from\": 4150, \"to\": 4164}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the Olympic uniform, representative of the gold standard for what competitive athletes strive for, is this ultra-skimpy version, then what does that say about how seriously we are thinking about the ramifications this could have for impressionable female runners?\", \"from\": 4205, \"to\": 4471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic uniform\", \"from\": 4208, \"to\": 4227}, {\"ngram\": \"representative\", \"from\": 4229, \"to\": 4243}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold standard\", \"from\": 4247, \"to\": 4264}, {\"ngram\": \"what competitive athletes\", \"from\": 4269, \"to\": 4294}, {\"ngram\": \"this ultra-skimpy version\", \"from\": 4310, \"to\": 4335}, {\"ngram\": \"the ramifications\", \"from\": 4403, \"to\": 4420}, {\"ngram\": \"impressionable female runners\", \"from\": 4441, \"to\": 4470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As an athlete, you are accustomed to thinking quite a bit about your body.\", \"from\": 4473, \"to\": 4547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 4476, \"to\": 4486}, {\"ngram\": \"quite a bit\", \"from\": 4519, \"to\": 4530}, {\"ngram\": \"your body\", \"from\": 4537, \"to\": 4546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What you put into it, how it feels during a workout or race, and almost inevitably, what it looks like.\", \"from\": 4548, \"to\": 4651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a workout\", \"from\": 4590, \"to\": 4599}, {\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 4603, \"to\": 4607}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For competitive runners, this often boils down to sinewy legs and defined abdominals.\", \"from\": 4652, \"to\": 4737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competitive runners\", \"from\": 4656, \"to\": 4675}, {\"ngram\": \"sinewy legs\", \"from\": 4702, \"to\": 4713}, {\"ngram\": \"defined abdominals\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ostensibly, this is an innocuous implication - if you expect to perform at a high level, there is a certain amount of physical conditioning that must be done.\", \"from\": 4738, \"to\": 4896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an innocuous implication\", \"from\": 4758, \"to\": 4782}, {\"ngram\": \"a high level\", \"from\": 4813, \"to\": 4825}, {\"ngram\": \"a certain amount\", \"from\": 4836, \"to\": 4852}, {\"ngram\": \"physical conditioning\", \"from\": 4856, \"to\": 4877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, spurred by a pervasive \\\"thinner is faster\\\" culture wherein struggles with body image are not only widely felt but also heavily normalized, a number of elite college and professional runners succumb to various disordered eating practices.\", \"from\": 4898, \"to\": 5144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"body image\", \"from\": 4981, \"to\": 4991}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 5046, \"to\": 5054}, {\"ngram\": \"elite college and professional runners\", \"from\": 5058, \"to\": 5096}, {\"ngram\": \"various disordered eating practices\", \"from\": 5108, \"to\": 5143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My team was no exception.\", \"from\": 5145, \"to\": 5170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My team\", \"from\": 5145, \"to\": 5152}, {\"ngram\": \"no exception\", \"from\": 5157, \"to\": 5169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout my time at Columbia, I watched many teammates and close friends devolve into full-fledged eating disorders, many of which stemmed from a desire to be as fast and fit as possible.\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my time\", \"from\": 5182, \"to\": 5189}, {\"ngram\": \"Columbia\", \"from\": 5193, \"to\": 5201}, {\"ngram\": \"many teammates\", \"from\": 5213, \"to\": 5227}, {\"ngram\": \"close friends\", \"from\": 5232, \"to\": 5245}, {\"ngram\": \"full-fledged eating disorders\", \"from\": 5259, \"to\": 5288}, {\"ngram\": \"a desire\", \"from\": 5317, \"to\": 5325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the Nike leotard is egregiously sparse, it's important to note that there are more than 25 style combinations for female athletes, a fact that many people outside the running community are not aware of.\", \"from\": 5362, \"to\": 5570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5372, \"end\": 5376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9933015277637895, \"rank\": 0.006743644348500694, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than 25 style combinations\", \"from\": 5446, \"to\": 5477}, {\"ngram\": \"female athletes\", \"from\": 5482, \"to\": 5497}, {\"ngram\": \"a fact\", \"from\": 5499, \"to\": 5505}, {\"ngram\": \"many people\", \"from\": 5511, \"to\": 5522}, {\"ngram\": \"the running community\", \"from\": 5531, \"to\": 5552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a far cry from the European Beach Volleyball Championship in 2021, when the Norwegian women's team wasfinedfor refusing to wear scanty bikini bottoms at the bronze medal game, opting instead to don shorts.\", \"from\": 5571, \"to\": 5781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5595, \"end\": 5633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Beach_Volleyball_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"European Beach Volleyball Championship\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Beach_Volleyball_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Beach_Volleyball_Championship\"}, {\"begin\": 5652, \"end\": 5661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9998417399872455, \"rank\": 0.00015828424955804994, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a far cry\", \"from\": 5576, \"to\": 5585}, {\"ngram\": \"scanty bikini bottoms\", \"from\": 5704, \"to\": 5725}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal game\", \"from\": 5729, \"to\": 5750}, {\"ngram\": \"shorts\", \"from\": 5774, \"to\": 5780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In leveling her own criticism at the leotard, American pole vaulter Katie Moon also underscored the multifarious outfit options, writing onInstagram,\\\"When you attack the buns and crop top saying something along the lines of it's 'sexist' (which if that was our only choice, it would be), even if it's with the best of intentions, you are ultimately attacking our decision as women to wear it.\\\"\", \"from\": 5783, \"to\": 6176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5829, \"end\": 5837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999998753992, \"rank\": 1.2456799111786445e-10, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 5857, \"end\": 5861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.84392466208485e-23, \"text\": \"Moon\", \"types\": [\"Q634\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her own criticism\", \"from\": 5795, \"to\": 5812}, {\"ngram\": \"the leotard\", \"from\": 5816, \"to\": 5827}, {\"ngram\": \"the multifarious outfit options\", \"from\": 5879, \"to\": 5910}, {\"ngram\": \"onInstagram,\\\"When\", \"from\": 5920, \"to\": 5937}, {\"ngram\": \"the buns\", \"from\": 5949, \"to\": 5957}, {\"ngram\": \"crop top\", \"from\": 5962, \"to\": 5970}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5978, \"to\": 5987}, {\"ngram\": \"the lines\", \"from\": 5994, \"to\": 6003}, {\"ngram\": \"'sexist\", \"from\": 6012, \"to\": 6019}, {\"ngram\": \"our only choice\", \"from\": 6040, \"to\": 6055}, {\"ngram\": \"intentions\", \"from\": 6101, \"to\": 6111}, {\"ngram\": \"our decision\", \"from\": 6142, \"to\": 6154}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 6158, \"to\": 6163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And if you honestly think that on the most important days of our careers we are choosing what we wear to appease the men watching over what we are most comfortable and confident in, to execute to the best of our abilities, that's pretty offensive,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 6178, \"to\": 6438, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most important days\", \"from\": 6213, \"to\": 6236}, {\"ngram\": \"our careers\", \"from\": 6240, \"to\": 6251}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\", \"from\": 6292, \"to\": 6299}, {\"ngram\": \"our abilities\", \"from\": 6387, \"to\": 6400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it comes to buns, the sentiment is somewhat mixed, too.\", \"from\": 6440, \"to\": 6500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"buns\", \"from\": 6457, \"to\": 6461}, {\"ngram\": \"the sentiment\", \"from\": 6463, \"to\": 6476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will start off by saying, there is absolutely nothing wrong with wearing them.\", \"from\": 6502, \"to\": 6582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"absolutely nothing\", \"from\": 6539, \"to\": 6557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are plenty of benefits to buns' small size and snappy waistband: many female runners find them to be more comfortable and feel that they stay in place better than traditional shorts.\", \"from\": 6583, \"to\": 6771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 6593, \"to\": 6599}, {\"ngram\": \"benefits\", \"from\": 6603, \"to\": 6611}, {\"ngram\": \"buns' small size\", \"from\": 6615, \"to\": 6631}, {\"ngram\": \"snappy waistband\", \"from\": 6636, \"to\": 6652}, {\"ngram\": \"many female runners\", \"from\": 6654, \"to\": 6673}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 6734, \"to\": 6739}, {\"ngram\": \"traditional shorts\", \"from\": 6752, \"to\": 6770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In college, I liked wearing buns during competitions.\", \"from\": 6773, \"to\": 6826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"college\", \"from\": 6776, \"to\": 6783}, {\"ngram\": \"buns\", \"from\": 6801, \"to\": 6805}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 6813, \"to\": 6825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gone were the middle-school days of flowy, parachute shorts that puffed at my thighs like a pastry.\", \"from\": 6827, \"to\": 6926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the middle-school days\", \"from\": 6837, \"to\": 6859}, {\"ngram\": \"flowy\", \"from\": 6863, \"to\": 6868}, {\"ngram\": \"parachute shorts\", \"from\": 6870, \"to\": 6886}, {\"ngram\": \"my thighs\", \"from\": 6902, \"to\": 6911}, {\"ngram\": \"a pastry\", \"from\": 6917, \"to\": 6925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Buns, though hardly a deviation from the bathing suits I wore during summer days at the Jersey Shore, legitimized my place in an elite group of Division I runners.\", \"from\": 6927, \"to\": 7090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Buns\", \"from\": 6927, \"to\": 6931}, {\"ngram\": \"hardly a deviation\", \"from\": 6940, \"to\": 6958}, {\"ngram\": \"the bathing suits\", \"from\": 6964, \"to\": 6981}, {\"ngram\": \"summer days\", \"from\": 6996, \"to\": 7007}, {\"ngram\": \"the Jersey Shore\", \"from\": 7011, \"to\": 7027}, {\"ngram\": \"my place\", \"from\": 7041, \"to\": 7049}, {\"ngram\": \"an elite group\", \"from\": 7053, \"to\": 7067}, {\"ngram\": \"Division\", \"from\": 7071, \"to\": 7079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Somewhat sanctimonious and totally brazen, they solidified my status and signified that I had \\\"made it\\\" as an athlete.\", \"from\": 7091, \"to\": 7209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my status\", \"from\": 7150, \"to\": 7159}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 7198, \"to\": 7208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It allowed us to showcase our bodies to the world just a bit more, as if to say, \\\"Thisis the standard, albeit often an unhealthy one, that you should aspire toward.\\\"\", \"from\": 7211, \"to\": 7376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 7222, \"to\": 7224}, {\"ngram\": \"our bodies\", \"from\": 7237, \"to\": 7247}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 7251, \"to\": 7260}, {\"ngram\": \"the standard\", \"from\": 7300, \"to\": 7312}, {\"ngram\": \"albeit often an unhealthy one\", \"from\": 7314, \"to\": 7343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This attitude is echoed extensively by women across the running community.\", \"from\": 7378, \"to\": 7452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This attitude\", \"from\": 7378, \"to\": 7391}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 7417, \"to\": 7422}, {\"ngram\": \"the running community\", \"from\": 7430, \"to\": 7451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a 2023New York Times featureon uniform expectations in women's running, Fleshman described buns as a \\\"badge of honor,\\\" a feeling the outlet noted was shared by more than a dozen interviewees at the collegiate and professional level.\", \"from\": 7453, \"to\": 7688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 2023New York Times featureon uniform expectations\", \"from\": 7456, \"to\": 7507}, {\"ngram\": \"Fleshman\", \"from\": 7528, \"to\": 7536}, {\"ngram\": \"buns\", \"from\": 7547, \"to\": 7551}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"badge\", \"from\": 7555, \"to\": 7563}, {\"ngram\": \"honor\", \"from\": 7567, \"to\": 7572}, {\"ngram\": \"a feeling\", \"from\": 7575, \"to\": 7584}, {\"ngram\": \"the outlet\", \"from\": 7585, \"to\": 7595}, {\"ngram\": \"more than a dozen interviewees\", \"from\": 7616, \"to\": 7646}, {\"ngram\": \"the collegiate and professional level\", \"from\": 7650, \"to\": 7687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The association between smaller, tighter uniforms and success can still be a double-edged sword for many, invoking both power and discomfort,\\\" wrote the Times' Nell Gallogly.\", \"from\": 7690, \"to\": 7865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The association\", \"from\": 7691, \"to\": 7706}, {\"ngram\": \"smaller, tighter uniforms\", \"from\": 7715, \"to\": 7740}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 7745, \"to\": 7752}, {\"ngram\": \"a double-edged sword\", \"from\": 7766, \"to\": 7786}, {\"ngram\": \"both power\", \"from\": 7806, \"to\": 7816}, {\"ngram\": \"discomfort\", \"from\": 7821, \"to\": 7831}, {\"ngram\": \"the Times' Nell\", \"from\": 7840, \"to\": 7855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But wearing form-fitting, barely there uniforms undeniably begets a host of negative consequences.\", \"from\": 7867, \"to\": 7965, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"form-fitting, barely there uniforms\", \"from\": 7879, \"to\": 7914}, {\"ngram\": \"a host\", \"from\": 7933, \"to\": 7939}, {\"ngram\": \"negative consequences\", \"from\": 7943, \"to\": 7964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The culture around buns at Columbia was unwaveringly steadfast, which is to say that if you were a middle-distance or long-distance runner (a group I oscillated between, events-wise) you wore them.\", \"from\": 7967, \"to\": 8164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The culture\", \"from\": 7967, \"to\": 7978}, {\"ngram\": \"buns\", \"from\": 7986, \"to\": 7990}, {\"ngram\": \"Columbia\", \"from\": 7994, \"to\": 8002}, {\"ngram\": \"a middle-distance or long-distance runner\", \"from\": 8064, \"to\": 8105}, {\"ngram\": \"a group\", \"from\": 8107, \"to\": 8114}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 8137, \"to\": 8143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like the Olympic team, we had the option to wear shorts instead; however, doing so was deemed odd.\", \"from\": 8165, \"to\": 8263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic team\", \"from\": 8170, \"to\": 8186}, {\"ngram\": \"the option\", \"from\": 8195, \"to\": 8205}, {\"ngram\": \"shorts\", \"from\": 8214, \"to\": 8220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wearing shorts was a choice saturated in quizzical, tight-lipped judgment.\", \"from\": 8264, \"to\": 8338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"shorts\", \"from\": 8272, \"to\": 8278}, {\"ngram\": \"a choice\", \"from\": 8283, \"to\": 8291}, {\"ngram\": \"quizzical, tight-lipped judgment\", \"from\": 8305, \"to\": 8337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe because of the optics of it all, a lack of uniformity, perhaps.\", \"from\": 8339, \"to\": 8408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the optics\", \"from\": 8356, \"to\": 8366}, {\"ngram\": \", a lack\", \"from\": 8376, \"to\": 8384}, {\"ngram\": \"uniformity\", \"from\": 8388, \"to\": 8398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But my hunch is that the style standard in elite running had become so entrenched that anything other than a few inches of fabric away from full-frontal was considered taboo.\", \"from\": 8409, \"to\": 8583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my hunch\", \"from\"