al\", \"from\": 8908, \"to\": 8910}, {\"ngram\": \"cellulite\", \"from\": 8932, \"to\": 8941}, {\"ngram\": \"her legs\", \"from\": 8945, \"to\": 8953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it wasn't just buns, either.\", \"from\": 8956, \"to\": 8988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just buns\", \"from\": 8970, \"to\": 8979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I experienced something similar after returning to campus my sophomore year, feeling slightly swollen from a second wave of puberty and the consequences of weightlifting.\", \"from\": 8989, \"to\": 9159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 9003, \"to\": 9012}, {\"ngram\": \"campus\", \"from\": 9040, \"to\": 9046}, {\"ngram\": \"a second wave\", \"from\": 9096, \"to\": 9109}, {\"ngram\": \"puberty\", \"from\": 9113, \"to\": 9120}, {\"ngram\": \"the consequences\", \"from\": 9125, \"to\": 9141}, {\"ngram\": \"weightlifting\", \"from\": 9145, \"to\": 9158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The skin-tight tank top we wore in races immediately made me feel insecure, but I told myself I had no recourse other than to shed a few pounds.\", \"from\": 9160, \"to\": 9304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The skin-tight tank top\", \"from\": 9160, \"to\": 9183}, {\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 9195, \"to\": 9200}, {\"ngram\": \"no recourse\", \"from\": 9260, \"to\": 9271}, {\"ngram\": \"a few pounds\", \"from\": 9291, \"to\": 9303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like the buns, nobody ever wore the loose-fitting tank top option.\", \"from\": 9305, \"to\": 9371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the buns\", \"from\": 9310, \"to\": 9318}, {\"ngram\": \"nobody\", \"from\": 9320, \"to\": 9326}, {\"ngram\": \"the loose-fitting tank top option\", \"from\": 9337, \"to\": 9370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These are hardly irrational concerns.\", \"from\": 9373, \"to\": 9410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hardly irrational concerns\", \"from\": 9383, \"to\": 9409}]}, {\"sentence\": 